Description:


Welcome to Chernarus. An open world of 225km Ã‚Â² located in a post-Soviet state and one of the area affected by a new, currently unknown infection which swept much of the world's population. You are one of the few that survived and now you should explore why this new wasteland in order to be able to fight for his life against what is left of the local population, now infected with the disease.
Play alone, or join with friends face to face the world as you choose your path in this brutal and chilling landscape using the means that you find along the way in order to survive.

DayZ has virtually no limits or time to finish, because even if you change the server information and items your character are saved in your profile and the game once you get on a different server your information is loaded and you are playing back the site where you left off on the previous server and all your items.
Of course, just like in real life if you die in the game just once all items and weapons obtained are lost and you must start over from scratch.


